```

This ONE command will:
- âœ… Analyze your project structure
- âœ… Create CLAUDE.md with project-specific docs
- âœ… Set up PM2 configuration (if multi-service)
- âœ… Update skill-rules.json for your paths
- âœ… Create dev docs structure
- âœ… Set up log directories

### For Task Documentation

```markdown
