### "Set up my monorepo with 3 services"

```markdown
I have a monorepo at ~/projects/my-app with:
- Backend API at ./services/api (Express)
- Auth service at ./services/auth (Express)
- React frontend at ./apps/web

Please analyze and set everything up.

/thomas-setup
```

### "I just need PM2 config"

```markdown
/thomas-setup --only pm2
```

### "Help me plan a new feature"

```markdown
I want to add user authentication with:
- JWT tokens
- Refresh tokens
- Password reset flow

Let's plan this out.

[Enter plan mode, then after plan is approved:]

/dev-docs user-authentication
```

### "Review my recent changes"

```markdown
/code-review recent changes
```

### "Skills aren't activating"

```markdown
I'm editing files in src/api but the backend skill isn't loading.

Can you check skill-rules.json and update the paths?
```

